response.overview: The Autobots continue to work for NEST, now no longer in secret. But after discovering a strange artifact during a mission in Chernobyl, it becomes apparent to Optimus Prime that the United States government has been less than forthright with them.
response.tagline: The invasion we always feared. An enemy we never expected.
response.title: Transformers: Dark of the Moon
